org.apache.dvsl
Interface DVSLNode

All Known Implementing Classes:
Dom4jNodeImpl
public interface DVSLNode

wrapper interface for nodes exposed in the template. Isolates the in-VSL DOM from that of the underlying implementation

Author:
Geir Magnusson Jr.
